          "type": "divider",
          "settings": {}
        },
        "subheading_QhB4a6": {
          "type": "subheading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What's in the box"
          }
        },
        "body_3": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>View the full list of packaging contents on the product page.</p>"
          }
        },
        "button_rF6dEJ": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
            "label": "Core 2 in the box",
            "button_size": "large",
            "icon_position": "none",
            "link": "shopify://products/core-2-practice-companion"
          }
        },
        "button_9nmwUx": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
            "label": "Spark in the box",
            "button_size": "large",
            "icon_position": "none",
            "link": "shopify://products/spark-practice-companion"
          }
        },
        "divider_3": {
          "type": "divider",
          "settings": {}
        },
        "subheading_fEQfTx": {
          "type": "subheading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Plus subscription"
          }
        },
        "image_BAXgF7": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {}
        },
        "body_4": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Upgrade your practice with Plus, our optional premium service that unlocks the full capabilities of our app. While the Core itself provides a complete experience on its own, Plus offers extras such as cloud storage of your songs and setlists, among other features. Our subscription model supports the rollout of multiple significant app updates annually, so get ready for a continuous stream of exciting new features!</p><p>Your Core comes with a free 3-month trial that you can redeem by following the in-app instructions after connecting your wearable!</p>"
          }
        },
        "divider_4": {
          "type": "divider",
          "settings": {}
        },
        "subheading_zLjb8j": {
          "type": "subheading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Charging the Core"
          }
        },
        "body_5": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>To charge your Core, attach the cable to the magnetic port located on the side of the device. The Core takes 1.5 hours to fully charge.</p><p><strong>Battery life</strong></p><ul><li>4+ days in watch mode, or</li><li>3+ hours metronome playback</li></ul><p><strong>Charging light</strong></p><ul><li>Orange light = charging</li><li>Green light = fully charged</li></ul>"
          }
        },
        "image_hPYJx3": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {}
        },
        "divider_5": {
          "type": "divider",
          "settings": {}
        },
        "subheading_C8GVdi": {
          "type": "subheading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "App & compatibility"
          }
        },
        "text_HPx7dM": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Before you can start using your Core, you need to unlock it in our app first. This helps us check if there are any firmware updates available. Download our app by clicking the buttons below, scanning the QR code or searching for “Soundbrenner” in the Google Play or iOS App Store.</p><p><strong>Download app</strong></p><p>The Metronome by Soundbrenner</p>"
          }
        },
        "heading_small_xffCmT": {
          "type": "heading_small",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "INSERT APP LINKS + QR CODE + THE LINK IN THE BUTTON BELOW"
          }
        },
        "text_4MqtCq": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Compatibility</strong></p><p>Requires an iPhone, iPad, iPod or Android device. More info on:</p>"
          }
        },
        "button_86rHwW": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
            "label": "Compatibility",
            "button_size": "large",
            "icon_position": "none",
            "link": "https://support.soundbrenner.com/hc/en-us/articles/900001230686-Soundbrenner-wearables-compatibility"
          }
        },
        "divider_6c6AAp": {
          "type": "divider",
          "settings": {}
        },
        "subheading_hhXcCi": {
          "type": "subheading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Wear & care"
          }
        },
        "text_KYQ8qF": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Core</strong></p><p>The Core is splash resistant (IP65). This means it can withstand light rain or water splashes, for example while washing your hands. However, it can not withstand heavy rain, showers or water immersion.</p><p>The Core contains strong magnets that may interfere with some medical devices. Read the \"Safety & regulatory information\" section at the end of this manual for more information.</p><h4>Tip</h4><p>Don't store your Core for extended periods (over 3 months) with an empty battery, as this can lead to permanent battery damage.</p>"
          }
        },
        "button_kaepFn": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
            "label": "Battery maintenance guide",
            "button_size": "large",
            "icon_position": "none",
            "link": ""
          }
        },
        "text_ecFNQA": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Silicone strap & body strap</strong></p><p>Both straps are very durable and suitable for all environmental conditions.</p><p><strong>Italian leather straps</strong></p><p>We only use premium quality leather sourced from Italy. Any variations in color or markings such as scars and wrinkles are inherent to the natural beauty and uniqueness of genuine leather.</p><p>Over time the leather will mold to your wrist and develop a patina finish. To maximize its durability, we suggest to limit the leather’s contact with moisture.</p>"
          }
        },
        "divider_ExTXVE": {
          "type": "divider",
          "settings": {}
        },
        "subheading_YbafmG": {
          "type": "subheading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Lock system for the rig"
          }
        },
        "text_HgaFMq": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>To remove the Core from its rig, twist it counterclockwise and take it off.</p>"
          }
        },
        "image_WAHFyi": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {}
        },
        "text_mfDFqP": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>To put the Core on its rig, hover it right above the rig and let go. Once the Core drops on the rig, it will magnetically snap into place.</p><p>When placing the Core on its rig, make sure the buttons point towards the direction of your hand. To wear the Core on your other wrist, you can change the orientation of the screen in our mobile app.</p><h4>Tip</h4><p>Make sure that you hear and feel the spring-loaded pin when the Core locks into place on the rig. This will ensure it can’t fall off.</p>"
          }
        },
        "divider_dn4KAP": {
          "type": "divider",
          "settings": {}
        },
        "subheading_k7g7gq": {
          "type": "subheading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Changing the watch straps"
          }
        },
        "text_NytJdp": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>To change your watch strap, simply turn the device on its back and open the two rivets on each side.</p><p>We’ve created a range of stylish strap options for the Soundbrenner Core and Spark. They’re made from the finest materials such as silicone, woven nylon or Italian leather. Explore our latest collection on:</p>"
          }
        },
        "button_xMyAQB": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
            "label": "Soundbrenner shop",
            "button_size": "large",
            "icon_position": "none",
            "link": "https://www.soundbrenner.com/shop"
          }
        },
        "image_66DxtJ": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {}
        },
        "divider_pCzwPk": {
          "type": "divider",
          "settings": {}
        },
        "heading_RV3Y7M": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Navigating the device"
          }
        },
        "subheading_rjzpdY": {
          "type": "subheading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Device overview"
          }
        },
        "image_rxgnT8": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {}
        },
        "divider_xADNhy": {
          "type": "divider",
          "settings": {}
        },
        "subheading_d3imP4": {
          "type": "subheading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Device controls"
          }
        },
        "text_dydTbg": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Top button</strong></p><ul><li>Go backward</li><li>Stop editing selection</li><li>Power on & power off (long press)</li></ul><p><strong>Bottom button</strong></p><ul><li>Go forward</li><li>Start editing selection</li><li>Open app dock</li></ul><p><strong>Wheel</strong></p><ul><li>Navigate the app dock</li><li>Change values while editing a selection</li></ul><p><strong>Touch surface</strong></p><ul><li>Tap the soundwave twice quickly to start or pause a feature while inside an app</li><li>Tap the soundwave three or more times to tap tempo while inside the \"Metronome\" app</li></ul>"
          }
        },
        "divider_8GrH8j": {
          "type": "divider",
          "settings": {}
        },
        "subheading_iL8Qey": {
          "type": "subheading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Power on & power off"
          }
        },
        "text_mkJcQC": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Power on</strong><br/>Hold the top button for 1 second to turn on the Core.</p>"
          }
        },
        "image_Dzc8kq": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {}
        },
        "text_9cDw6H": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Power off</strong></p><p>1. Hold the top button for 3 seconds until the power off prompt appears.</p>"
          }
        },
        "image_fnMLty": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {}
        },
        "text_6Kej6h": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>2. Select yes, by pressing the bottom button.</p>"
          }
        },
        "divider_xrGQeX": {
          "type": "divider",
          "settings": {}
        },
        "subheading_8r8K8r": {
          "type": "subheading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Navigation hierarchy"
          }
        },
        "image_bxUAQc": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {}
        },
        "divider_JgwgWY": {
          "type": "divider",
          "settings": {}
        },
        "subheading_UTgFBp": {
          "type": "subheading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Touch interactions"
          }
        },
        "text_VAA3iK": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The Core features a capacitive touch surface. To ensure it can reliably detect your inputs, make sure that you use two fingers flat across the surface. Don’t just use your fingertips!</p><p><strong>Start or pause a feature</strong></p><p>Tap the soundwave twice quickly to start or pause certain features. Works in \"Metronome\" app, \"Timer\" app, \"Stopwatch\" app and the \"Smartphone music remote\".</p>"
          }
        },
        "image_mgU7ky": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {}
        },
        "text_4aafcq": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Tap tempo</strong></p><p>Tap the soundwave three times or more at a steady pace. The Core will set a new tempo that matches the average pace of your taps. Works in \"Metronome\" app only.</p>"
          }
        },
        "image_UGq7br": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {}
        },
        "divider_eGmUQA": {
          "type": "divider",
          "settings": {}
        },
        "subheading_rcLpyC": {
          "type": "subheading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Time, date & status icons"
          }
        },
        "text_kBrneM": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Time notation</strong></p><p>Use the app to change the time notation from AM/PM to 24h clock and vice versa.</p><p><strong>Watch face icons</strong></p>"
          }
        },
        "image_J9tiAi": {
          "type": "image",
